    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distributional records of twelve species of freshwater planarians in the Iberian Peninsula. Data from De Beauchamp, 1920; De Beauchamp, 1932; Baguñà et al. 1980, 81; Gourbault, 1981; Ribas, 1990; Sluys et al. 1995; Carranza & Giribet, 1997; unpublished records, this study." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/206801/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.206808>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Phagocata gallaeciae (A) specimen from the River Miño after Belesar dam, living animal, (B – C) holotype, V. Pl. 6870.1, (B) sagittal reconstruction of the copulatory apparatus (anterior to the left), (C) sagittal section of the copulatory apparatus (anterior to the left), (D) V. Pl. 6871.2, sagittal reconstruction of the copulatory apparatus (anterior to the left)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/206808/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

